---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="About">
  <h1>About</h1>

  <div class="intro" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
    <p>
      I'm Lucas Beillo, a data analyst based in A Coruña, Galicia, with 4+ years of experience across
      data engineering, analysis, and visualization in both public and private sectors. I design ETL/ELT
      pipelines, run data-quality processes, and build BI dashboards in Power BI and Tableau that turn
      messy data into decisions people actually act on.
    </p>
    <p>
      Some of the work I'm proudest of: modelling 300k+ cadastral records in PostgreSQL/PostGIS for
      municipal clients, and building scraping and data-quality pipelines that monitored 50+ international
      e-commerce platforms while cutting manual work by 60%. I'm comfortable in Scrum teams and have
      a background in environmental engineering and geospatial data — a useful edge, not the headline.
    </p>
    <p>
      Originally from Brazil, I came into data through engineering — first cartographic, then environmental
      at UNESP — before moving fully into analytics. Currently pursuing a Master's in Computer Engineering
      at UNED, and building Recolle, a civic-tech app for geolocated incident reporting.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Experience</h2>
    <div class="card-list">
      <div class="card" style="display: block; cursor: default;">
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem;">
          <span class="card-title">Geopixel</span>
          <span class="card-meta">2024–2026</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-meta" style="margin-top: 0.15rem;">Bauru, Brazil</div>
        <div class="card-desc" style="margin-top: 0.35rem;">
          Data analyst — modelled 300k+ cadastral records across 4 municipalities in PostgreSQL/PostGIS,
          and built Power BI dashboards for citizen-service and operational tracking
        </div>
        <div class="card-tags" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
          <span class="tag">PostgreSQL/PostGIS</span><span class="tag">Power BI</span><span class="tag">Python</span><span class="tag">QGIS</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="display: block; cursor: default;">
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem;">
          <span class="card-title">Ethercity</span>
          <span class="card-meta">2021–2024</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-meta" style="margin-top: 0.15rem;">São Paulo, Brazil</div>
        <div class="card-desc" style="margin-top: 0.35rem;">
          Data analyst — built scraping and data-quality pipelines monitoring 50+ e-commerce platforms
          (3,000+ URLs/day), cutting manual work 60% through automation; Tableau dashboards, Scrum team
        </div>
        <div class="card-tags" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
          <span class="tag">Python</span><span class="tag">Pydantic</span><span class="tag">MySQL</span><span class="tag">MongoDB</span><span class="tag">Tableau</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="display: block; cursor: default;">
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem;">
          <span class="card-title">Geobase</span>
          <span class="card-meta">2021</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-meta" style="margin-top: 0.15rem;">Presidente Prudente, Brazil</div>
        <div class="card-desc" style="margin-top: 0.35rem;">Geoprocessing — rural property georeferencing, environmental records (CAR), spatial data QA</div>
        <div class="card-tags" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
          <span class="tag">QGIS</span><span class="tag">AutoCAD</span><span class="tag">cartography</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="display: block; cursor: default;">
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem;">
          <span class="card-title">Aerocarta</span>
          <span class="card-meta">2013</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-meta" style="margin-top: 0.15rem;">São Paulo, Brazil</div>
        <div class="card-desc" style="margin-top: 0.35rem;">Cartography and photogrammetry — mapping production</div>
        <div class="card-tags" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
          <span class="tag">cartography</span><span class="tag">photogrammetry</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Education</h2>
    <div class="card-list">
      <div class="card" style="display: block; cursor: default;">
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem;">
          <span class="card-title">Máster en Ingeniería Informática</span>
          <span class="card-meta">2025–2027</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-desc">UNED · A Coruña, Spain · In progress</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="display: block; cursor: default;">
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem;">
          <span class="card-title">Environmental Engineering</span>
          <span class="card-meta">2016–2023</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-desc">
          UNESP · Presidente Prudente, Brazil. TFG: spatio-temporal analysis of vegetation cover and
          surface temperature in Bauru using Google Earth Engine. PIBIC: water-quality index via
          multivariate analysis
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Certifications</h2>
    <ul style="list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.4rem;">
      <li class="muted">CS50: Introduction to Computer Science <span class="mono">— Harvard / edX</span></li>
      <li class="muted">Databricks Fundamentals <span class="mono">— Databricks</span></li>
      <li class="muted">dbt Fundamentals <span class="mono">— dbt Labs</span></li>
      <li class="muted">Data Warehousing <span class="mono">— Snowflake University</span></li>
      <li class="muted">Claude Code 101 <span class="mono">— Anthropic</span></li>
      <li class="muted">Google Analytics Individual Qualification <span class="mono">— Google</span></li>
      <li class="muted">Full-Stack ML with Metaflow <span class="mono">— Outerbounds</span></li>
      <li class="muted">Automatizaciones Web: Selenium, Selenoid, Docker</li>
      <li class="muted">Google Earth Engine for Water Resources Management</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Languages</h2>
    <p class="mono muted">Portuguese (native) · Spanish (C2) · English (C1)</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      <a href="mailto:lucas.beillo@live.com">lucas.beillo@live.com</a> ·
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/lucasbeillo/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a> ·
      <a href="https://github.com/beillo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</Base>
